                <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, hsl(var(--elegant-teal)), hsl(var(--elegant-mint))); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem;">üí¨</div>
